cat << EOF
The Video Decode and Presentation API for Unix (VDPAU) provides a complete
solution for decoding, post-processing, compositing, and displaying compressed
or uncompressed video streams. These video streams may be combined (composited)
with bitmap content, to implement OSDs and other application user interfaces.
EOF
